Jai gets hounded by the internal investigation team at ATU over his recent unauthorised escapades that put a dangerous criminal like Roshan Sherchand on the streets. Meanwhile, the ATU is able to pinpoint Roshan's hideout, and sends a crack team to apprehend him. Jai leads the ATU team into Roshan's hiding place and manages to retrieve a crucial piece of evidence, that is, there are not one but six virus bombs in the city and the first one is going off in one hour!
